{"tid":2443620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個人生最後悔的事 。。。","createTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T09:56:56.000Z","uid":123335,"like":33,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6b9a60cb2c483eeda7f070f47a728964d14d3706","tid":2443620,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:00.000Z","msg":"我先，<br />\n當年中學開始暗戀一個女仔<br />\n直到讀緊大學果陣，已暗戀 7 年，<br />\n但其間個女仔一直唔知，我亦冇任何暗示，<br />\n只係間中搵下佢 sms /msn 傾計 <br />\n但佢份人就好靜態，e.g. 煲韓劇<br />\n而我就鍾意運動既， e.g. 做 gym 跑步 <br />\n其實大家都冇咩共同話題，唔太岩傾 .... <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果陣我諗，<br />\n「我自己竟然可以暗戀同一個女仔 7 年 ？？？」<br />\n「咁專一既男人邊度搵？？？」<br />\n<br />\n果個 Moment 突然間覺得自己好撚型，好撚心雄<br />\n就突然間搵佢間示愛，<br />\n點知一示愛就收好人卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db937cb0371907ff4ea76467a90d78006fece3a","tid":2443620,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"real"},{"pid":"36bb80f6593f95d1355a60b52f7e61b9052f461d","tid":2443620,"uid":375958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"real"},{"pid":"663b3b901b9d3e7d9e0cc4c670a117ae44c10cfe","tid":2443620,"uid":375958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5db937cb0371907ff4ea76467a90d78006fece3a","tid":2443620,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"real"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:21:30.000Z","msg":"慢咗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e673ef2d0070681ea2dd07dc5e1758194760527","tid":2443620,"uid":90646,"like":3,"